<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>About LawGPT - Instructions & Credits</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root {
      /* Theme from your existing project */
      --bg-color: #0b1f3a;       /* Deep Navy Blue */
      --card-bg: #112d52;        /* Slightly lighter for contrast */
      --text-main: #e0e6ed;      /* Off-white */
      --accent: #7bbcff;         /* Muted Light Blue */
      --highlight: #60a5fa;      /* Soft Cyan for links/focus */
      --btn-hover: #0088cc;      /* Telegram Blue for hover */
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--text-main);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Skip Link for Accessibility */
    .skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px;
      left: 0;
      background: var(--highlight);
      color: #000;
      padding: 8px;
      z-index: 100;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .skip-link:focus { top: 0; }

    header {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .logo-img {
      height: 50px;
      width: auto;
    }

    nav a {
      color: var(--text-main);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    nav a:hover, nav a:focus {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg-color);
    }

    main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    section {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid #1f4068;
    }

    h1, h2 { color: var(--accent); margin-top: 0; }
    h3 { color: var(--text-main); border-bottom: 1px solid #1f4068; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 20px; }
    
    .icon-heading {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .icon-small {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
    }

    ul, ol { padding-left: 20px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

    /* Keyboard Shortcut Keys styling */
    kbd {
      background: #061221;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      font-family: monospace;
      color: var(--highlight);
    }

    /* Specific Telegram Button Styling */
    .telegram-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg-color);
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      margin: 15px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    
    .telegram-btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--btn-hover);
      color: white;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .telegram-btn svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      fill: currentColor;
    }

    code {
      background-color: #061221;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--highlight);
      font-family: monospace;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
      border-top: 1px solid #1f4068;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>

  <header role="banner">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <img src="/Images/law-gpt-logo.png" alt="LawGPT Logo: A shield with a balance scale" class="logo-img" />
      <h1>About LawGPT</h1>
    </div>
    <nav aria-label="Main Navigation">
      <a href="/chat" aria-label="Go to Chat Bot">Open Chat Bot</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content">
    
    <section aria-labelledby="intro-heading">
      <div class="icon-heading">
        <img src="/Images/justice_scale_icon.svg" alt="" class="icon-small" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2 id="intro-heading">Who We Are</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        <strong>LawGPT</strong> is an accessible AI legal assistant designed to make Indian Law easy to understand for everyone.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Creator:</strong> Siddharth Kalantri from Bhiwandi.</li>
        <li><strong>Mission:</strong> To bridge the gap between complex legal texts and common citizens using AI.</li>
        <li><strong>Knowledge Base:</strong> Constitution of India and Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita (BNS) 2023.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="web-instructions">
      <div class="icon-heading">
        <img src="/Images/mic_icon.svg" alt="" class="icon-small" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2 id="web-instructions">How to Operate (Web Chat)</h2>
      </div>
      <p>The web chat is designed for accessibility and ease of use.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Typing:</strong> Type your legal question in the text box.</li>
        <li><strong>Sending:</strong> Click the "Send" button or press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Enter</kbd>.</li>
        <li><strong>Old vs New Laws:</strong> By default, the bot uses new BNS 2023 laws. To ask about old laws, simply type "IPC" in your question (e.g., <em>"What is IPC 302?"</em>).</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="telegram-instructions">
      <div class="icon-heading">
        <img src="/Images/telegram_bot_icon.svg" alt="" class="icon-small" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2 id="telegram-instructions">Connect with SmartBot</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        You can access our legal assistant directly on your mobile or desktop app via Telegram or Unigram.
      </p>

      <a href="https://t.me/SmartBotGiver_bot" target="_blank" class="telegram-btn">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm5.894 8.221l-1.97 9.28c-.145.658-.537.818-1.084.508l-3-2.21-1.446 1.394c-.16.16-.295.293-.605.293l.214-3.054 5.56-5.022c.24-.213-.054-.334-.373-.121l-6.869 4.326-2.96-.924c-.64-.203-.658-.64.135-.954l11.566-4.458c.538-.196 1.006.128.832.942z"/>
        </svg>
        Open SmartBot in Telegram
      </a>

      <h3>How to Find Manually (Unigram / Telegram)</h3>
      <p>If the button above does not open the app automatically, follow these steps:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Open the <strong>Telegram</strong> or <strong>Unigram</strong> app on your device.</li>
        <li>Tap the <strong>Search icon</strong> (üîç) usually located at the top right.</li>
        <li>Type the exact username: <code>@SmartBotGiver_bot</code></li>
        <li>Look for the bot named <strong>smartbot</strong> (it may say "created by Siddharth Kalantri" in the bio).</li>
        <li>Select it and tap the big <strong>Start</strong> button to begin chatting.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer role="contentinfo">
    <p>Law made accessible through AI. &copy; 2025 LawGPT.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>